    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per the MRL 2 assessment plan. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within the 20% acceptance band across all five operating conditions, and the RH < 1 criterion relative to the predicate device is satisfied. The assessment team accepts this model for the stated context of use.",
